{"tid":470240,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"《3日2夜》辣火頭 傳有違「禁奶令」即炒","createTime":"2017-11-16T06:07:05.000Z","updateTime":"2017-11-18T04:38:10.000Z","uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"80519a2f136424f6a229b655040e41bd5e6b188e","tid":470240,"uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-16T06:07:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20171115/large/1510747979_b6a4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20171115%2Flarge%2F1510747979_b6a4.jpg&h=32cff9c4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20171115/large/1510735773_eff6.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20171115%2Flarge%2F1510735773_eff6.jpg&h=f4ba27c0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20171115/large/1510735774_4d41.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20171115%2Flarge%2F1510735774_4d41.png&h=1ff09bb6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n今日大台突然傳出「禁奶令」，眾說紛紜。有知情人士透露，禁奶令由董事局主席「殼王」陳國強親自落指令。<br />\n<br />\n早於幾星期前，佢已同高層們密斟，直至噚晚先向台幕後發出「禁奶令」，有指因為想節目同直播APP可打入大陸巿場，所以要嚴禁女藝人「倒奶」，無論劇集劇情抑或J2嘅旅遊節目都唔可以太出位。'<br />\n<br />\n《蘋果》收到消息，稱如有幕後製作或女藝人唔聽指引犯禁，即炒。<br />\n<br />\n今次呢次相信最大影響就係J2嘅《3日2夜》。呢個節目喺2014年8月開始，喺網上人氣非常之咁高，原因？無他嘅，節目中有唔少新晉主持帶住去旅行，其中一班女主持仲不時大晒比堅尼呀、浸下溫泉騷quali咁，網民當然大飽眼福。<br />\n<br />\n據知，今次「禁奶令」嘅起因正正就因為《3日2夜》，有傳大台高層覺得呢個節目過火，但係又唔想俾人覺得矛頭直指某一個節目／監製，所以突然頒佈呢個禁令。<br />\n<br />\n不過講法眾說紛紜，亦有傳因為除咗上述原因外，有人覺得某高層太得寵，製作方法有問題，但冇人敢出聲，結果其他人終於忍唔住，搵機會同董事局主席反應，而主席亦下旨「禁奶令」，而今次可以話係挫某高層銳氣！<br />\n<br />\n至於「禁令」中列明，如果只係得一個女藝人出trip，就需要有藝員科女同事陪同。呢個指引，消息稱係針對《3日2夜》成team出trip時，不時只得女藝人及幕後出發，未必每次都有女工作人員隨行。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.entertainment.appledaily.com/entertainment/realtime/article/20171115/57461430\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.entertainment.appledaily.com%2Fentertainment%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20171115%2F57461430&d=6VEn%2FPYJ85EMFqQXFeGs4cVakpCEQgWe3bOYm8oES40%3D&h=02388478\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.entertainment.appledaily.com%2Fentertainment%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20171115%2F57461430&h=3b248e8f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.entertainment.appledaily.com/entertainment/realtime/article/20171115/57461430</a>"},{"pid":"7ce60c6577a238ddb95f109fe6334767f6cca3ad","tid":470240,"uid":46943,"like":4,"dislike":2,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-16T06:19:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://static.stheadline.com/stheadline/inewsmedia/20171116/_2017111611545465041.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.stheadline.com%2Fstheadline%2Finewsmedia%2F20171116%2F_2017111611545465041.jpg&h=64b56c84&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n以後得返呢啲"},{"pid":"a4efa866913ea1a341665f3eee457c82a4a9ea42","tid":470240,"uid":48796,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-16T06:30:58.000Z","msg":"ViuTV 同 奇妙電視<br />\n重唔叫你哋旗下女藝員瘋狂倒奶 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6f366331ab10797b78333067f0ba45f4450201e5","tid":470240,"uid":28031,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-16T07:15:53.000Z","msg":"陳婉痕班奶星搵哂碼頭未 失業啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"be4d8cb2fe0a3e861c82642f5e69b464332afa7e","tid":470240,"uid":44454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-16T07:18:19.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"http://static.stheadline.com/stheadline/inewsmedia/20171116/_2017111611545465041.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.stheadline.com%2Fstheadline%2Finewsmedia%2F20171116%2F_2017111611545465041.jpg&h=64b56c84&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n以後得返呢啲</blockquote><br />\n呢啲唔係奶呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"54e01a4263888d273